This paper is likely to belong to the arXiv CS sub-category of Natural Language Processing (cs.CL) as it deals with named entity recognition, which is a common task in NLP. The use of deep structured models also suggests a focus on machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Additionally, the paper involves the integration of multiple datasets, which could fall under the sub-categories of information retrieval (cs.IR) and natural language understanding (cs.NE).
